{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "孟星魂来到马方中家，发现院子里四具尸体——马方中、马月云和两个孩子全部身亡。他仔细验尸后发现，致命伤并非刀伤，而是先中了剧毒再补一刀，推断这是马方中为了守住老伯的秘密而主动让全家服毒自尽。一个不明身份的邻居来打听马车之事，孟星魂以冷厉态度盘问对方后将其骗进屋内发现尸体，借此消除后患。与此同时，在井底密室中，老伯与凤凤的关系逐渐缓和。凤凤为老伯切咸肉烙饼，两人以轻松幽默的方式谈论男女之道。凤凤的态度从冷嘲转为讨好，她意识到在密室中只有两人相依为命，唯有让老伯开心自己才能活得更好。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你找谁？",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我是来找马大哥的，他在不在？",
      "tone": "赔笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你找他干什么？",
      "tone": "审问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "昨天晚上有个人将马大哥的两匹马和车子赶走了，到现在还没回来，我想来问问马大哥，究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "嗫嚅",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "赶车的是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "是个块头很大的人。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "车子里面有没有别人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "有多少人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "怎么会不知道……",
      "tone": "沉下脸",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "车窗和车门都是紧紧关着的，我看不见。",
      "tone": "口吃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "既然看不见，怎知道有人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "看那赶车的样子，绝不像是赶着辆空车。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "他是什么样子？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "看样子他很匆忙，而且还有点惊慌。",
      "tone": "讷讷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你什么时候看到他的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "昨天晚上。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "昨天晚上什么时候？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "已经很晚了，我已经准备上床的时候。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "既然已那么晚，你怎么还能看得清楚？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我……我并没有看得很清楚。",
      "tone": "口吃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "既然没有看清楚，怎么知道他很惊慌？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我……我……我只不过有那种感觉而已。",
      "tone": "口吃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你亲眼看到那辆马车？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你看到车子往哪条路走的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "就是这条路。",
      "tone": "指路",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你会不会记错？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "车子一直没有回头？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "所以我才想来问问马大哥，这是怎么回事，那两匹马他一向都看得很宝贵，无论多好的朋友，想借去溜个圈子都不行，这次怎么会让一个陌生人赶走的呢？",
      "tone": "赔笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "那大块头不是这里的人？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "绝不是，这里附近的人，我就算不认得，至少总见过。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "那人你没见过？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "从来没有。",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "他赶走的是你的马？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不是，是马大哥的！",
      "tone": "回答",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "人，你不认得，马，又不是你的，这件事和你有什么关系？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "没……没有。",
      "tone": "退后",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "既然和你没有关系，你为什么要来多管闲事？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你知不知道多管闲事的人，总是会有麻烦上身的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "喝止",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "大……大爷还有何吩附？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "你是不是来找马大哥的？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "他就在里面，你为什么不进去找他了？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_ju",
      "speaker_name": "邻居",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我……我怕……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_lin_ju",
      "text": "怕什么？快进去，他正在里面等你。",
      "tone": "沉着脸",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "看来你刀法不错。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "可惜只不过是菜刀。",
      "tone": "嫣然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "我总觉得女人惟一应该练的刀法，就是切菜的刀法，对女人来说，这种刀法简直比五虎断门刀还有用。",
      "tone": "眨眼",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "五虎断门刀最多也只不过能要人的命，但切菜的刀法有时却能令一个男人终生拜倒在你脚下，乖乖地养你一辈子。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "我本来总认为你只不过还是个孩子，现在才知道你真的已是个女人。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "有人说，女为悦己者容，也有人说，女为己悦者容，我觉得这两句话都应该改一改。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "怎么改法？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "应该改成，女为悦己者下厨房。",
      "tone": "眨眼笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "女人若是不喜欢你，你就算要她下厨房去炒个菜，她都会有一万个不愿意的。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "不错，女人只肯为自己喜欢的男人烧好菜，这的确是千古不移的大道理！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "就好像男人只肯为自己喜欢的女人买衣服一样，他若不喜欢你，你即使要他买块破布送给你，他都会嫌贵的。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "但我知道有些男人虽然不喜欢他的老婆，还是买了很多漂亮衣服给老婆穿。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "那只因他根本不是为了他的老婆而买的！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "是为了谁呢？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "是为了他自己，为了他自己的面子，其实他心里恨不得他老婆只穿树叶子！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "我若要你替我买衣服，你肯不肯？",
      "tone": "眼波流动",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "当然肯！",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "你会为我买怎样的料子做衣服？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "树叶子，最好的树叶子！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "那么你以后也只有吃红烧木头了。",
      "tone": "撅嘴",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "红烧木头？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "你让我穿树叶子，我不让你吃木头？吃什么呢？",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "你刚才还在拼命地想让我生气，现在怎么变了？",
      "tone": "大笑后",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "我变了吗？",
      "tone": "眨眼",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "现在你不但在想法子让我多吃些，而且还在尽量想法子要我开心。",
      "tone": "笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "这也许因为我已想通了一个道理。",
      "tone": "叹气",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "什么道理？",
      "tone": "问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "这屋子里只有我们两个人，你若很不开心，我也一定不会很好受，所以我若想开心些，我一定要先想法子让你开心。",
      "tone": "凝视",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_feng",
      "speaker_name": "凤凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_bo",
      "text": "一个人无论在什么情况下都应该尽量想法子使自己活得开心些，你说是不是？",
      "tone": "慢慢道",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_bo",
      "speaker_name": "老伯",
      "listener": "char_feng_feng",
      "text": "想不到你已变得愈来愈聪明了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    }
  ],
